Your problem is not about Lambda expressions! Your problem is that you are mocking on

    when(httpSecurity.authorizeRequests(any(Customizer.class))).thenReturn(httpSecurity);
and 

    when(httpSecurity.oauth2ResourceServer(any(Customizer.class))).thenReturn(httpSecurity); 

These mocks make it so that the Code in your class is not executed because they are mocked. By *removing* these two lines you should see your lines covered (or getting an error in the beginning :) ).

